OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Ftonight with plenty of clear spells,
OL,7,Fhowever cloud will linger in places. A
OL,8,Fwarm and humid night with temperatures
OL,9,Fremaining in double figures across the
OL,10,Fregion.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FA largely dry and bright day
OL,13,Fwith plenty of sunny spells. A small
OL,14,Fchance of a few light showers later in
OL,15,Fthe afternoon. Feeling hot and
OL,16,Fincreasingly humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
